{"tid":114302,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"專家點評 - 沈振盈 大時代2.0料難出現","createTime":"2017-02-09T16:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T13:54:26.000Z","uid":62896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a98965022901b31c610242df5fad0475cd64fd5d","tid":114302,"uid":62896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈在ontv財經節目《股壇MasterMind》表示，恒指今日繼續走高，突破23,400點阻力穩守23,500點，他估計後市有機會衝上24,000點但未必可守住，除非有內地政策及A股配合，而且現時外圍其實有很多不利消息充斥，未必可見大時代2.0出現。<br />\n<br />\n資金今日流入航運股，他表示要注意最近多個落後板塊突然爆升後，均各有發展，一些升後回軟，一些則升完再升，似乎現時沒有客觀條件令股市彈起，相信升勢會在2至3日內完結，投資者要小心行事，連環向上未必對後市好，想入市也要尋找一些已經落後的板塊，例如電力、基建股等等。<br />\n<br />\n對於青島啤酒(00168)或獲嘉士伯青睞，他認為青啤業務穩健，有固定網絡銷售，現適宜短炒，長遠要看基本因素及業績。詳情請收看ontv東網電視財經新聞。"},{"pid":"494eb6c56c65ae78f7cfa760daff8548bfd4f2d5","tid":114302,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"青島今次瀨野，有貨既師兄快走"},{"pid":"560ef98199f92b9dc9fc546bfb4f66d3f1915e82","tid":114302,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw 大師見到咁多徒弟po 佢d 聖喻一定好安慰。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42913760da1e34bdb5f03351b8710462613df807","tid":114302,"uid":17765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"168 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c352c52c448aec06b632cdaf55613b5186aa47c1","tid":114302,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:19:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港股大時代再臨 指日可待</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1df116a8cc1c718d55f693d5ba49fd3